data.description: Gorgeous town home in a convenient and desirable Fairburn neighborhood. As you enter you are greeted by upgraded luxury vinyl flooring throughout the main, a large light-filled living room with stone surround fireplace. The open floor plan leads you to the dining room and spacious kitchen which features a breakfast bar, updated white cabinets, newer hardware and pantry offering ample storge space. A half bath and laundry closet complete the first level. Upstairs the spacious primary suite features two walk-in closets and an ensuite bath with garden tub and separate shower. Secondary bedrooms are generously sized with large closets. The private fenced in backyard is perfect for entertaining. Newer privacy fence in the backyard and the playset can even be included at buyer's request. Excellent location, near the highway with access to nearby shopping centers, eateries, and everything you need! Minutes from the airport, interstate, and Atlanta Metro Studios. Don't miss this great opportunity in South Fulton.A Must See!
